      • getSecretSeriesFor

        protected Optional<SecretSeries> getSecretSeriesFor(org.jooq.Configuration configuration,
                                                    Client client,
                                                    String secretName)
        Parameters:
        client - client to access secrets
        secretName - name of SecretSeries
        Returns:
        Optional.absent() when secret unauthorized or not found. The query doesn't distinguish between these cases. If result absent, a followup call on clients table should be used to determine the exception.
